snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 Official Gameplay Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Embody a Space Marine of the Ultramarines Chapter, a superhuman warrior who protects humanity from untold horrors, in brutally efficient third-person action as you take on the massive Tyranid hordes.

Take a look at a brand new glimpses of gameplay for the upcoming action-packed blockbuster Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 soon to be released on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S and PC.

#warhammer40k #warhammerskulls #gaming
